==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Use one's eyes for the large areas, use one's hands for smaller areas.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: dà chù zhúo yăn, xĭao chù zhúo shŏu

===Idiom===
'''[[大]][[處]][[著]][[眼]]，[[小]][[處]][[著]][[手]]'''

# Keep the general goal in sight, while taking hold of the daily tasks.
# [[Keep one's eye on the ball]], while not [[loose sight of the forest for the trees|loosing sight of the forest for the trees]].

===Alternate forms===
[[大处着眼，小处着手]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

